OL,3,CJust Stop Oil disrupt Sigourney
OL,4,CWeaver's The Tempest performance
OL,6,FJust Stop Oil disrupted a West End
OL,7,Fperformance of The Tempest starring
OL,8,FSigourney Weaver on Monday night.
OL,10,FTwo members of the climate protest
OL,11,Fgroup walked on stage carrying a sign
OL,12,Fthat read: "Over 1.5 degrees is a
OL,13,Fglobal shipwreck."
OL,15,FHayley Walsh, a 42-year-old lecturer
OL,16,Fand mother of three, and Richard Weir,
OL,17,Fa 60-year-old mechanical engineer,
OL,18,Flaunched a confetti cannon during the
OL,19,Fperformance, and said: "we'll have to
OL,20,Fstop the show ladies and gentlemen,
OL,21,Fsorry".
