OL,6,FProtestors interrupted the performance
OL,7,Fat the Theatre Royal Drury Lane and
OL,8,Fwas captured in a video shared on
OL,9,Fsocial media
OL,11,FWeaver, 75, who was sat on stage at
OL,12,Fthe time, was escorted off as the
OL,13,Fcrowd responded with a mixture of boos
OL,14,Fand some cheers.
OL,16,FThe protesters' message referenced the
OL,17,Frecent announcement that 2024 has been
OL,18,Fthe warmest year on record globally,
OL,19,Fwith average temperatures surpassing
OL,20,Fthe critical threshold of 1.5C above
OL,21,Fpre-industrial levels.
