OL,6,FWalsh later explained why she decided
OL,7,Fto protest, saying she fears for her
OL,8,Fchildren's future and is frustrated
OL,9,Fover the lack of meaningful action on
OL,10,Fclimate change despite years of
OL,11,Fpersonal efforts.
