OL,11,FHe warned that unless fossil fuel use
OL,12,Fis phased out by 2030, the impacts of
OL,13,Fthe crisis on homes, crops, and
OL,14,Fneighborhoods will only worsen.
OL,16,FThe protest briefly halted the
OL,17,Fperformance, but Weaver later returned
OL,18,Fto the stage.
